sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant Tenants as /api/tenants
    participant Onboarding as TenantOnboardingAppService
    participant Provisioner as MongoTenantProvisioner
    participant Master as SaasMasterDb
    participant TenantDb as tenant_{id}
    participant OAuthApi as /api/oauth-clients
    participant OAuthService as OAuthClientAppService

    Admin->>Tenants: POST criar tenant + adminEmail
    Tenants->>Onboarding: CreateTenantAsync
    Onboarding->>Provisioner: ProvisionAsync
    Provisioner->>Master: Criar Tenant + chave RSA protegida
    Provisioner->>TenantDb: Criar schema, SMTP e templates
    Provisioner->>TenantDb: Inserir OAuthClient owner
    Note over Provisioner,TenantDb: client_id=client_{tenantId}, secret com hash PBKDF2, scope owner
    Provisioner-->>Onboarding: tenantId + clientId + clientSecret puro
    Onboarding-->>Admin: tenant criado + oauthClientId

    Admin->>OAuthApi: POST /api/oauth-clients com Bearer owner
    OAuthApi->>OAuthApi: Policy OAuthClientsWrite
    OAuthApi->>OAuthService: CreateAsync(tenantId, request)
    OAuthService->>OAuthService: Validar tokenConfig, redirect URIs e scopes
    OAuthService->>TenantDb: Inserir OAuthClient ativo
    OAuthService-->>Admin: clientId + clientSecret retornado uma única vez
